reviewText: My now five year old loved this show when it was on Qubo channel. It features a mouse and his best friend rabbit. They have many adventures with all of their other friends; a set of Geese triplets, an very friendly alligator named Jasper, Edwina the elephant, Hazel the squirrel, and Thunder the Rhino!! There is a lesson to be learned in every episode and its very entertaining. I really wished they'd make more children's' shows like this!!
